		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />The PCE had an unreleased keyboard for its unreleased Modem/BASIC/Graphics editor:<br /><br /><img src="http://www.chrismcovell.com/secret/1990/TsushinKeyboard.jpg" alt="Image" /><br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://www.chrismcovell.com/TsushinBooster/index.html">http://www.chrismcovell.com/TsushinBooster/index.html</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Incidentally, the emulator Mednafen supports the PCE keyboard's protocol, since the Tsushin Booster ROM had detection code for it.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
