		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Yeah, mednafen supports the keyboard in emulation. I wanted to make a tracker program for the PCE (on the real hardware) that could use it (that, and a Dungeons of Daggorath port). I was thinking a modern keyboard to PCE keyboard scan code converter. Maybe something akin to an atmel mcu. The PCE already has an official mouse; the two would be great together.

		

		</td>
